import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import Alert from './Alert'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"alert"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#alert"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Alert`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __code={`<Alert text="This is a the default Alert." />`} __scope={{props,Alert}}>
  <Alert text="This is a the default Alert."/>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"props"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#props"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Props`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Alert} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"types"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#types"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Types`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={2} __code={`<Alert type="success" text="success" />
<Alert type="warning" text="warning" />
<Alert type="danger" text="danger" />
<Alert type="info" text="info" />`} __scope={{props,Alert}}>
  <Alert type="success" text="success"/>
  <Alert type="warning" text="warning"/>
  <Alert type="danger" text="danger"/>
  <Alert type="info" text="info"/>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"theme-config-props"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#theme-config-props"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Theme config props`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`These configs applies to all Alert elements on the application`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre">{`// Changes default alert font size
alertFontSize:  @Number - [Default: 13]
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag></MDXTag>
